Package: mcasm
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, ${python:Depends}
Provides: ${python:Provides}
Description: Microcode assembler for homebrew CPUs.
 This package provides a microcode macro-assembler (macros provided by cpp)
 which helps build microcode ROM images for home-designed CPUs and other state
 machines of similar complexity.
 .
 Output is in various formats, including binary images, C files and Verilog.
